    "Click to show options for filtering your time entries. You can filter by date range or status." : "Click to show options for filtering your wpisy czasu. You can filter by date range or status.",
    "Click to start your break. German labor law requires breaks after 6 hours of work." : "Click to start your przerwa. niemieckie prawo pracy requires przerwas after 6 hours of work.",
    "Click to update your time entry. The form will be validated before saving." : "Click to update your wpis czasu. The form will be validated before saving.",
