    "This is the last calendar day in each year when carryover from the opening balance (Resturlaub) may still be used for vacation. You enter each person's opening balance per calendar year under Users. After this date, new vacation requests can only use the annual vacation entitlement from the working time model\u2014not carryover. This applies to everyone." : "This is the last kalendarz day in each year when carryover from the opening saldo (Resturlaub) may still be used for urlop. You enter each person's opening saldo per kalendarz year under Users. After this date, new urlop requests can only use the annual urlop entitlement from the czas pracy model\u2014not carryover. This applies to everyone.",
